From: fast-code <fast-code@local>
Subject: [PATCH] Remove 8 non-essential notification hooks from REPL render cycle

Hooks removed:
  1. useNpmDeprecationNotification     - irrelevant (not npm-installed)
  2. useCanSwitchToExistingSubscription - network call every session
  3. useModelMigrationNotifications     - one-time migration notices
  4. useInstallMessages                 - installation checks irrelevant
  5. usePluginAutoupdateNotification    - auto-update disabled
  6. useIDEStatusIndicator              - 26 cache slots, heaviest hook
  7. useTeammateLifecycleNotification   - swarm mode only
  8. useAutoModeUnavailableNotification - behind TRANSCRIPT_CLASSIFIER flag

Estimated per-render savings: 38 React hook slots eliminated.
---
 src/screens/REPL.tsx | 24 ++++++++++++------------
 1 file changed, 12 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

